Download MNIST dataset and store in PATH_TO_STORE_TESTSET(PATH_TO_STORE_TRAINSET)/MNIST/raw/ with format -ubyte, -ubyte.gz

Create a conda environment from yml:
1. conda env create -f environment.yml
2. conda activate ifm

Command for Gaussian experiment full sweep:
1. python Gaussian_sweep.py

Command for Noised MNIST experiment full sweep:
2. python MNIST_sweep.py

To run a single experiment without doing the full sweep, choose a single set of hyperparameters and a specific algorithm
